Package: helpR
Type: Package
Title: Miscellaneous helper and SAS/Stata duplicate functions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Craig", "McGowan", email = "mcgowan.cj@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description:
  Helper functions for tasks such as making print-friendly bivariate 
  tables, sample size flow counts, and more. Also contains R approximations
  of some common, useful SAS/Stata functions.
